		</li><li class="SG_j_linedot1"><p class="atcTitCell_tit SG_dot"><a suda-uatrack="key=blog_tjblog&value=h_tjblog" title="正在热议106“海外就医”遍地" target="_blank" href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4b2286d50102yed8.html?tj=2?tj=2">正在热议106“海外就医”遍地</a></p>
        <p class="atcTitCell_nm"><a suda-uatrack="key=blog_tjblog&value=h_tjblog" target="_blank" href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/1260553941" class="SG_linkb"></a></p>
		</li>		</ul>
		<div id="atcPicList">
